		<h3>Scenario Builder</h3>

		<p>Begin understanding your plant in new ways. Streamlyne builds relationships between assets, sensors, and new user-generated input so you can track what is going on, when it's going on, and why it's going on through graphical visualizations. As Streamlyne collects daily information from your systems you can begin tracking the anomolies in processes that may be devastating to your plant. Use this information to create safety standards, process limits, historical references, situation alerts, and reports to share.  </p>

