				<h3>Alerts</h3>
				<p>Streamlyne is constantly reading and analyzing data through our algorithms to alert you before things go wrong. Instantly be alerted when assets are reaching maximum or minimum thresholds, the probabilities of malfunction, and the liklihood of a negative event happening. You can also see what other assets may be affected to monitor them as well.
